was 7000 books they found

00:58:25.310 --> 00:58:29.230
on witchcraft in one
of these things.

00:58:29.230 --> 00:58:33.590
And I assured her, I said, I
think that this is a blowup

00:58:33.590 --> 00:58:38.480
that someone wants to criticize
the project from other directions

00:58:38.480 --> 00:58:40.430
to say that there [laughter].

00:58:40.430 --> 00:58:43.690
But, anyway, that says it.

00:58:43.690 --> 00:58:46.790
&gt;&gt; I was just going to say that
those of us who are bibliophiles,

00:58:46.790 --> 00:58:49.840
