this room I think are, you know,

00:58:49.840 --> 00:58:54.760
value our book as a book if the
binding, the smell, the print,

00:58:54.760 --> 00:58:57.750
and so forth -- but it
seems to me in an age

00:58:57.750 --> 00:59:03.680
